cdm_source_name: Safety and Efficacy of the XanomelineTransdermal Therapeutic System (TTS) in Patients with Mild to Moderatealzheimer's disease.
source_description: Safety and Efficacy of the XanomelineTransdermal Therapeutic System (TTS) in Patients with Mild to Moderatealzheimer's disease. Trial Primary Objective: To determine if there is a statistically significant relationship between the change in both ADAS-Cog and CIBIC+ scores, and drug dose (0, 50 cm2 [54 mg], and 75 cm2 [81 mg]). Trial Primary Objective: To document the safety profile of the xanomeline TTS.
